snippet.title: Rocket League Season 11 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Rocket League Season 11 Gameplay Trailer!
Learn more here: https://www.rocketleague.com/season-11

This Season we’re celebrating soccar with one giant party! Get behind the wheel of the drift-ready Nissan Silvia. When you’re not powersliding around the new Estadio Vida Arena, fill your garage with dozens of vibrant Rocket Pass rewards.

Need something for your party playlist? How about the song in this trailer! Monstercat is bringing Brazilian flavor to Rocket League with “Não Sei Parar” by Bhaskar & Afterclapp. The full song comes out June 8, and you’ll be able to get it as a Player Anthem in the Item Shop! Presave the song here: https://monster.cat/naoseiparar

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSeason11 #RocketLeagueTrailer
